author: Second Wind
description:
This video is brought to you by Hounded, the upcoming dog adventure game where you follow your nose to find your master. Head on over to its Kickstarter page to learn more today. – https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/houndedgame/hounded

This week on Firelink, KC, Marty, and Nick chat about the Switch 2 launch, the steps they took to secure hardware, and early impressions of the launch lineup.

Keep up to date on the standings of our Firelink Fantasy Critic Draft -- https://www.fantasycritic.games/league/6093c943-c06e-4f44-8206-157e410d7914/2025

If you dig the podcast, considering supporting us over at Patreon --  https://www.patreon.com/SecondWindGroup

title: Nintendo Switch 2: Day One Impressions | Firelink Podcast
